                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I don't quite understand the changes needed to existing applications to work with this revision.\r\n\r\nAfter i updated one application to 19571 the modules resources stopped loading.\r\n\r\nBy example i had a Text_Model_Text class which is not loading anymore, and of course all the classes from modules are failing loading.\r\n\r\nBefore of this i was using:\r\n\r\nresources.modules[] = \"\"\r\n\r\nAnd Bootstrapper as:\r\n\r\nclass Text_Bootstrap extends Zend_Application_Module_Bootstrap\r\n{\r\n\r\n} \r\n\r\nfor each module...",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-12-11T01:24:51.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-12-11T01:24:51.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/36860",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Can you elaborate?\r\n\r\nThe only thing this is supposed to do is allow specifying a module autoloader for the application-level bootstrap; this is done by simply adding a key to your configuration:\r\n{code}\r\nappnamespace = \"Application\"\r\n{code}\r\nModule bootstraps should be unaffected; am I to understand that your module bootstraps are no longer initializing module autoloaders? (I'm a bit unclear as to what you're asking...)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-12-11T06:50:15.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-12-11T06:50:15.000+0000"
                },
                {
